		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <p class="- topic/p ">As used in this subpart-</p>
			      <p class="- topic/p ">“Leasing” means the acquisition of motor vehicles, other than by purchase from private or commercial sources, and includes the synonyms “hire” and “rent.”</p>
			      <p id="id193QE0110SX" class="- topic/p ">“Motor vehicle” means an item of equipment, mounted on wheels and designed for highway and/or land use, that-</p>
